summary: Removes wind sound from Archmage Quarters, adds music.
descriptionHtml:
Sunnie\'s Archmage\'s Quarters Audio Enhancement

Version: v1.0
Release date: Dec 27, 2011


What: This mod removes the wind tunnel effect in the Archmage\'s Quarters at the College and adds 5 random ambient tavern tunes to the room.


To install: Unpack and drop the Sunnie_AMQ_NoWindTunnel.esp into Skyrim\'s data folder (?\\Steam\\SteamApps\\common\\skyrim\\Data\\). Activate mod with a mod manager or the games launcher.
To uninstall: Delete Sunnie_AMQ_NoWindTunnel.esp from the Skyrim data folder (?\\Steam\\SteamApps\\common\\skyrim\\Data\\).

Note: You may have to exit and enter the cell 2 or 3 times before any previous saved settings are purged and the new data takes over.


Confilcts: This mod is not compatible with Archmage Quarters part of \"Female bard for you house\" by stsg.
It will also conflict with any other mod that modifies the ambient sound or the area music in the Archmage\'s Quarters.


Permissions: You can not use this mod or any part of it in another mod without permission. This mod can not be uploaded to any server or host site not authorized by the author. At the time of publish, the only authorized site/host is The Skyrim Nexus Site (e.g. skyrimnexus.com).
author: Sunnie
